item.description:
Seacoast Liberty group has been rocking the seacoast for a year. Let's celebrate!!

There will be snacks. Bring some more if you want.

BYOB

For those who are actually interested in watching the game, it will be on in a separate room, insulated from the shenanigans and tomfoolery of those not interested in the game.

See you there!
item.name: Happy Anniversary Seacoast Liberty/Superbowl Party!!
